{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":false,"flaws":{},"title":"Storage.length","mdn_url":"/de/docs/Web/API/Storage/length","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Web_Storage_API\">Web Storage API</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Storage\"><code>Storage</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Eigenschaften</summary><ol><li><em><code>length</code></em></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Methoden</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Storage/clear\"><code>clear()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Storage/getItem\"><code>getItem()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Storage/key\"><code>key()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Storage/removeItem\"><code>removeItem()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Storage/setItem\"><code>setItem()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Ähnliche Seiten zu Web Storage API</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/StorageEvent\"><code>StorageEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Window/localStorage\"><code>Window.localStorage</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Window/sessionStorage\"><code>Window.sessionStorage</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p>Die <code>length</code>-Eigenschaft der <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Storage\"><code>Storage</code></a>-Schnittstelle enthält die Anzahl der im <code>Storage</code>-Objekt gespeicherten Datensätze.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Syntax","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">var <em>aLength</em> = <em>Storage</em>.length;</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"rückgabewert","title":"Rückgabewert","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Ein Integer.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"beispiel","title":"Beispiel","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Die folgende Funktion fügt drei Datensätze hinzu und liest abschließend die Anzahl der vorhandenen Datensätze:</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">populateStorage</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  localStorage<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">setItem</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'bgcolor'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'yellow'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  localStorage<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">setItem</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'font'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'Helvetica'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  localStorage<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">setItem</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'image'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'cats.png'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n  localStorage<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>length<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// sollte 3 zurückgeben</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect1\">\n<p><strong>Hinweis</strong>: Weitere Beispiele sind im 